Nestled in Trinity Bellwoods Park, located West of Bathurst Street and just North of Queen Street, Trinity Community Recreation Centre offers a variety of programs for all ages. The open concept building lends itself to an array of community events taking place all year long. The centre's new gym floor is about 5000 square feet and has a resilient hardwood maple floor with rubber pads. Preschool, school age, youth and adult programs are offered seasonally both within the centre and in Trinity Bellwoods Park. Come join us today!<br><br>
